high_descs: Walk to the stove top behind you
Grab the pan off of the stove top
Take the pan to the sink behind you
Place the pan in the sink, turn the faucet on, then turn it off
Take the pan out of the sink, take it back to the stove top
Place the pan on the bottom right burner on the stove top
anns.task_desc: Clean the pan, place it on the stove top.

high_descs: Pick up the pan from the stove.
Bring the pan to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Bring the pan to the stove.
Put the pan on the front of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Clean the pan, put it back on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and stop and face the stove
Grab the pan that is on the top right of the stove
Turn right twice and stand in front of the sink
Place the pan in the sink to wash it
Grab the pan from the sink and turn left twice to get to the stove
Place the pan on the right of the stove
anns.task_desc: Putting a clean pan on the stove
